char_171_bldsk_CN_013.voiceText: ...Are you even listening? We're having trouble collecting rare blood types for the emergency blood bank. So—what? What did you just say? A promotion? Now?
char_171_bldsk_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_171_bldsk_CN_014.voiceText: This only means more work for me from now on, right? I knew this would happen! I'm an expert in this field after all. Don't worry, I can handle it!
char_171_bldsk_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_171_bldsk_CN_017.voiceText: Wait, I need to prepare my medical equipment first.

char_171_bldsk_CN_018.voiceText: A leader only needs to report to you, right?

char_171_bldsk_CN_019.voiceText: The medical equipment is ready. We can start any time.

char_171_bldsk_CN_020.voiceText: I don't know much about the enemy at the moment. I have my hands full with all these injured Operators...

char_171_bldsk_CN_022.voiceText: The medical equipment has been set up.

char_171_bldsk_CN_023.voiceText: If you're injured, call for help immediately!

char_171_bldsk_CN_029.voiceText: It's really nerve-wracking being in the medic squad. Support troops are really under lots of pressure! Good thing I'm already used to it.

char_171_bldsk_CN_030.voiceText: The battlefield is a place of tragedy. I hope they come to understand this one day.

char_171_bldsk_CN_031.voiceText: Help the injured first. And the enemies who got away, we'll get them another day.

char_171_bldsk_CN_032.voiceText: Sorry, we didn't bring enough backup medicine...

char_171_bldsk_CN_033.voiceText: I guess I'm more accustomed to figuring things out myself...

char_171_bldsk_CN_036.voiceText: Doctor, isn't it almost time for your annual checkup?

char_002_amiya_CN_002.voiceText: Dr. Kal'tsit told me you have to be 100% focused on your work to maximize efficiency. So... yes, that's what I'm gonna do!

char_002_amiya_CN_003.voiceText: Rhodes Island is in normal sailing mode. Doctor, can you sort out our heading for me?

char_002_amiya_CN_004.voiceText: As the leader of Rhodes Island, there's still a lot I need to learn. I hope you will guide me on our path to the future.

char_002_amiya_CN_005.voiceText: Maybe it's just my wishful thinking, but I hope Rhodes Island can be a second home to everyone.
char_002_amiya_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_002_amiya_CN_006.voiceText: We've lost so much that's dear to us to make it so far. Sometimes, I can't help but ask myself... is it really worth it?
char_002_amiya_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_002_amiya_CN_007.voiceText: Sometimes I remember my hometown... cold, the air smelling like rusted copper. Rhodes Island is such a cozy place in comparison... So I have to do everything I can to protect this oasis.
char_002_amiya_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_002_amiya_CN_008.voiceText: Hehe... I picked up the violin again. I was thinking I might surprise everyone at our next party. So please, Doctor, don't tell anyone yet.
char_002_amiya_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_002_amiya_CN_009.voiceText: We've still got a long, long way to go, Doctor. This might be a journey without an end, but as long as you're with me, everything's all right.
char_002_amiya_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_002_amiya_CN_010.voiceText: There's still lots of work that needs to be done, Doctor. You can't rest now!

char_002_amiya_CN_011.voiceText: Doctor, I'm so glad that we're back together. And we'll walk this path together! I've got your back if you've got mine.

char_002_amiya_CN_012.voiceText: I see... thank you, Doctor! Your guidance is truly helpful.

char_002_amiya_CN_013.voiceText: I'm so excited to fight by your side again, Doctor!
char_002_amiya_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_002_amiya_CN_014.voiceText: What I saw that day... the despair stuck in my throat, the futile attempts to scream... I want to bury it all deep inside my mind and never let it out again...
char_002_amiya_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_002_amiya_CN_029.voiceText: No matter how difficult the mission, we can handle it as long as you're here, Doctor. That's what I've always believed.

char_002_amiya_CN_030.voiceText: We may have achieved a perfect victory, but we still can't let our guard down.

char_002_amiya_CN_031.voiceText: Good job, Doctor! Get some rest. You must be tired.

char_002_amiya_CN_032.voiceText: I'm fine... Get it together, everyone!

char_002_amiya_CN_033.voiceText: You want something to drink, Doctor?

char_110_deepcl_CN_001.voiceText: Good morning, Doctor. Can I paint a portrait of you? And don't worry, I'll try not to... bring it to life. Besides, I'm not capable of bringing EVERYTHING to life, you know!

char_110_deepcl_CN_002.voiceText: I feel like I'm not supposed to appear here...

char_110_deepcl_CN_003.voiceText: Doctor... what color are you, reflected in my eyes?

char_110_deepcl_CN_004.voiceText: There are lots of fun creative resources here at Rhodes Island! I'm feeling inspired...

char_110_deepcl_CN_005.voiceText: See my adorable "assistants"? Oh, you think they're scary? No way! They're the cutest babies!
char_110_deepcl_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_006.voiceText: Ha, so this is your color? Look into my eyes, then... paint me in your colors.
char_110_deepcl_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_007.voiceText: That's right. Even if no one understands me, I'll continue to make art. No matter what monsters my works turn into...
char_110_deepcl_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_008.voiceText: We artists are a unique breed... we get stuck at least thirty days a month and think everything we produce is garbage. Also, we only become inspired after midnight.
char_110_deepcl_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_009.voiceText: The battered world, paint peeling, finally closes its eyes in its dark depths—that's right, darkness is the true color of the ocean. Black is the only color you see, you say? Wait till I share all I know with you...
char_110_deepcl_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_010.voiceText: Are you... dreaming? Is the world in your dreams as colorful as the beings in this world, Doctor?...

char_110_deepcl_CN_011.voiceText: I'm Deepcolor, a painter. That's right, just a "painter", nothing more.

char_110_deepcl_CN_013.voiceText: Um, could you just... stop caring about me? If you keep treating me like this... like I matter... I-I don't know what will become of me...
char_110_deepcl_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_014.voiceText: Thank you, Doctor. Now, let's complete this piece of art, shall we?
char_110_deepcl_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_110_deepcl_CN_017.voiceText: Me? Going to battle? Are you nuts?

char_110_deepcl_CN_018.voiceText: I can't lead that many people.

char_110_deepcl_CN_025.voiceText: No need to be in such a hurry.

char_110_deepcl_CN_027.voiceText: You gotta get past my "assistants" first.

char_110_deepcl_CN_028.voiceText: Can you defeat these little ones?

char_110_deepcl_CN_029.voiceText: If you really make me mad... you won't want to know what happens next.

char_110_deepcl_CN_030.voiceText: I need to sketch these victorious heroes.

char_110_deepcl_CN_031.voiceText: Aw, got my clothes dirty again...

char_110_deepcl_CN_032.voiceText: If only the end of the battle could be erased and redone, like a sketch.

char_110_deepcl_CN_033.voiceText: This room's got a nice design.

char_110_deepcl_CN_036.voiceText: Doctor, since we happen to have some time off, wanna see my newest work?

char_166_skfire_CN_001.voiceText: The fire alarm's blaring? Sorry, must be because I was passing by your office. It… it causes my body to heat up, you know…

char_166_skfire_CN_002.voiceText: There's no language that's impossible to learn, no Arts that are impossible to understand. Isn't that the truth, plain and simple? …What? I'm the exception to the rule, you say?

char_166_skfire_CN_003.voiceText: My life plans? …Tch, it was all going swimmingly until that dreadful attack. But after Reunion murdered Phil, their eradication moved up to the top of my to-do list.

char_166_skfire_CN_004.voiceText: Rhodes Island's methods aren't nearly tough enough. They'll only drag King's Wand down.

char_166_skfire_CN_005.voiceText: Can you talk to Amiya for me? Poor girl, her kind heart clouds her judgment. As far as I'm concerned, total annihilation is the only fitting end for an undesirable.
char_166_skfire_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_166_skfire_CN_006.voiceText: Your current skills can't compare to even the average level of a King's Wand member such as myself. Ha, right, I'm powerful… and the power of all five of us put together… words can't begin to describe.
char_166_skfire_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_166_skfire_CN_007.voiceText: Shichiyou's blade was a gift from Shiro. Heard that the former owner before Shiro was a swordsmaster who could fell all the cherry blossoms of the Far East with a single swing. But even that legendary swordsmaster was no match for Shiro and had to surrender the blade.
char_166_skfire_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_166_skfire_CN_008.voiceText: What happened to your shirt? What? I burned it? But… impossible… my self-control is impeccable, I think…? I… well, I'm sorry. Really sorry.
char_166_skfire_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_166_skfire_CN_009.voiceText: We might be on opposite ends of the spectrum when it comes to ideals, but I do enjoy watching the people of Rhodes Island sweating away with bright hopes for the future. Yep, that's a compliment. It's a heartwarming sight.
char_166_skfire_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_166_skfire_CN_010.voiceText: How lazy. So you think it's fine to just sleep here and waste away the precious day?

char_166_skfire_CN_011.voiceText: I am Skyfire of King's Wand. I will remain at Rhodes Island until my objective is accomplished. What's my objective, you ask? To burn every last Reunion thug to ashes, of course.

char_166_skfire_CN_012.voiceText: This is no way to force me to unleash my true power.

char_166_skfire_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_166_skfire_CN_014.voiceText: Ha. Enjoying the privileges I deserve from time to time is a good way to relax.
char_166_skfire_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_166_skfire_CN_017.voiceText: The battlefield needs some heating up.

char_166_skfire_CN_018.voiceText: The rays of the sun are my shield.

char_166_skfire_CN_020.voiceText: Kneel before the flame of the heavens.

char_166_skfire_CN_023.voiceText: Bad luck is always lying in wait for the weak.

char_166_skfire_CN_024.voiceText: The wise always take the initiative.

char_166_skfire_CN_027.voiceText: The flames of the sun shall devour you!

char_166_skfire_CN_028.voiceText: The rays of the skies will set you aflame!

char_166_skfire_CN_029.voiceText: There is no soul that can survive the sunflame.

char_166_skfire_CN_030.voiceText: Pathetic... you're nothing but ashes now. Not a trace left behind.

char_166_skfire_CN_032.voiceText: No way... impossible... how could I have...

char_166_skfire_CN_033.voiceText: Can't you prepare a room with a lower temperature for me?

char_166_skfire_CN_034.voiceText: Are you trying to get your hand burnt?

char_166_skfire_CN_036.voiceText: Doctor, can you explain this theory to me? All I need is 12 minutes of your time.

char_240_wyvern_CN_002.voiceText: The two seniors from the BPRS squad are here too? Then... can I join their squad in the future?

char_240_wyvern_CN_003.voiceText: Huff... huff... three more sets of physical training and I'll be half-done for today! Doctor... please... fetch my water bottle for me…

char_240_wyvern_CN_004.voiceText: My hometown? It's... a cruel wilderness. Survival itself is a difficult feat. Compared to that, Rhodes Island is like heaven.

char_240_wyvern_CN_005.voiceText: I've become stronger than when I was an intern for Blacksteel.
char_240_wyvern_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_240_wyvern_CN_007.voiceText: The 22nd rule of Blacksteel: "Anyone who loses her weapon no longer belongs here." That's why I always bring my hellebarde with me wherever I go. What? The rule doesn't apply to everyday situations, you say? But... if I remember correctly... wait, let me check. "This rule only applies to contracted Operators and new recruits under training." Hm, Ms. Franka didn't tell me about this part.
char_240_wyvern_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_240_wyvern_CN_008.voiceText: Instructor Dobermann must be a secret sadist! How could she expect me to deal with all those live Originium slugs alone? I... I just can't!
char_240_wyvern_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_240_wyvern_CN_009.voiceText: I think I know now why Franka and Liskarm like being at Rhodes Island so much. Compared to Blacksteel, it's more... home-y here. And besides exciting missions, there are lots of fun places to explore...
char_240_wyvern_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_240_wyvern_CN_010.voiceText: Shh, quiet. The Doctor is resting!

char_240_wyvern_CN_011.voiceText: I'm Vanilla, trainee Operator. Nice to meet you, Doctor.

char_240_wyvern_CN_012.voiceText: It's time to organize my notes. This way, I can better digest what I've just learned!

char_240_wyvern_CN_013.voiceText: A... promotion medal? For me? Th-thank you!
char_240_wyvern_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_240_wyvern_CN_018.voiceText: Could I... really be a good leader?

char_240_wyvern_CN_020.voiceText: I won't bring shame to everyone in Blacksteel!

char_240_wyvern_CN_026.voiceText: This axe isn't just for show!

char_240_wyvern_CN_027.voiceText: Battles aren't always won by the most experienced!

char_240_wyvern_CN_031.voiceText: If we worked a bit harder, we could have done better.

char_240_wyvern_CN_032.voiceText: I… I'm still not strong enough...

char_240_wyvern_CN_036.voiceText: Doctor, want to eat dinner together?

char_236_rope_CN_001.voiceText: Doc~tor~, you didn't forget anything, did you?

char_236_rope_CN_002.voiceText: Picking pockets to feed myself? Yeah, that was how I grew up. I didn't exactly have a choice... I'd have died otherwise.

char_236_rope_CN_003.voiceText: For a grappling hook to be sturdy, choosing a good rope is the key. Hm? Why do I like my grappling hook so much, you ask? Well, duh... try scaling a building with your bare hands and you'll see.

char_236_rope_CN_004.voiceText: Fine, fine, I'll listen to everything you say from now on, Doctor! Can I go back to my room now? I'm really busy! All right, all right, just stop nagging, ugh...

char_236_rope_CN_005.voiceText: If it weren't for you and your people, Doctor, I'd probably still be locked up. Say, how did you find me anyway? You heard people talking about how talented I am? Huh.
char_236_rope_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_236_rope_CN_006.voiceText: There are actually lots of ways to survive in the slums... it's just that... there are also lots of people who don't survive. I never really had a choice. I hope you understand, Doctor.
char_236_rope_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_236_rope_CN_007.voiceText: My parents kicked me out and I had to fend for myself on the streets. I'm way better off at Rhodes Island than back in the gutter, huh?
char_236_rope_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_236_rope_CN_008.voiceText: A lot of people died from this same disease. I kinda gave up, and thought the same thing would happen to me until I ended up at Rhodes Island... Thank goodness you people found me. But be honest, Doctor, you'll cure me, right? If you can't... I guess that's fine too.
char_236_rope_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_236_rope_CN_009.voiceText: I used to go days without eating sometimes. Now, I get regular meals, so Rhodes Island is alright in my book. Hm? You want me to thank you? Come on, haven't I thanked you enough already?
char_236_rope_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_236_rope_CN_010.voiceText: Ugh, this chair... damn it... it's... kinda comfy...

char_236_rope_CN_011.voiceText: The name's Rope, nice to meet ya. Oh, here's your ID card, don't forget it. Huh? Why do I have it? That's a se-cret!

char_236_rope_CN_012.voiceText: Would something like this actually work?

char_236_rope_CN_013.voiceText: Let's talk cash! Dough! Who cares about a promotion? I need that paper!
char_236_rope_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_236_rope_CN_014.voiceText: Yeah! Now that I got paid, I guess I can work hard.
char_236_rope_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_236_rope_CN_018.voiceText: I'm gonna be captain? I'd have asked for a hardship bonus, but I'll let it slide this time since it's you.

char_236_rope_CN_019.voiceText: Look at the map and figure out your route before we get in there. This is experience talking.

char_236_rope_CN_020.voiceText: Hey, do you think they're hauling some good loot?

char_236_rope_CN_021.voiceText: I don't really do straight-up fights.

char_236_rope_CN_022.voiceText: Put me to good use, o-k-a-y?

char_236_rope_CN_028.voiceText: Once I hook you, you're not getting away.

char_236_rope_CN_029.voiceText: That one was more exciting than usual. More profitable too.

char_236_rope_CN_030.voiceText: It'd be a waste to leave all that good stuff here. The dead guys don't need 'em, right?

char_236_rope_CN_031.voiceText: Some of 'em got away? Yeah sure. They might turn over a new leaf, who knows.

char_236_rope_CN_032.voiceText: ...Erm, I'm gonna bug out now. You coming? Life is precious!

char_236_rope_CN_033.voiceText: Is there an air vent in this room? Nothing, just curious.

char_236_rope_CN_036.voiceText: I'd like to learn what it's like to be a normal girl sometime. But... maybe I just can't?

char_237_gravel_CN_001.voiceText: Aaaahhh! You want me to stay by your side? I can barely keep my heart in my chest!

char_237_gravel_CN_003.voiceText: Don't mind me, just continue with your work.

char_237_gravel_CN_004.voiceText: Hmm? What am I looking at? Why, you, of course!

char_237_gravel_CN_005.voiceText: If that's what you ask, Doctor, I will do what it takes to become stronger.
char_237_gravel_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_237_gravel_CN_006.voiceText: Ahaha... You won't need to worry about any ambushes or assassination attempts. Because I'll aaalways be here with you.
char_237_gravel_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_237_gravel_CN_007.voiceText: Are you finally... a little bit interested in me now? Well, I've always been a big bit interested in you!
char_237_gravel_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_237_gravel_CN_008.voiceText: Thanks for taking such good care of me these days. By my knighthood of Kazimierz, I hereby pledge to repay your kindness with my life—huh? You're not used to me talking this way? I'm an honest-to-goodness knight! I've memorized so many lines like this.
char_237_gravel_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_237_gravel_CN_009.voiceText: It's been a while since anyone was this kind to me, after I turned up in Kazimierz. So... if you'll have me, Doctor... On my honor as a knight, I, Gravel—I mean, Senomy, shall serve you always at your side.
char_237_gravel_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_237_gravel_CN_010.voiceText: When I'm here with you, don't you feel your heart racing?

char_237_gravel_CN_011.voiceText: Mmmwah. Hm? What's wrong? Your face is beet red. That's just how I say hello. Don't think too much about it. Anyway, I'm Gravel, a knight of Kazimierz. It's a pleasure.

char_237_gravel_CN_012.voiceText: Are you the one who comes up with all Rhodes Island's battle tactics, Doctor? That's sooo interesting, hehe...

char_237_gravel_CN_013.voiceText: You think I'm doing well, Doctor? Yaay!
char_237_gravel_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_237_gravel_CN_014.voiceText: This means you need me, doesn't it?
char_237_gravel_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_237_gravel_CN_017.voiceText: You want to go together? Hehe...

char_237_gravel_CN_027.voiceText: You really think you'll get away?

char_237_gravel_CN_029.voiceText: Of course the Doctor's tactics are flawless~

char_237_gravel_CN_030.voiceText: My blade hasn't even been stained red yet... hehe...

char_237_gravel_CN_031.voiceText: Run! Run all you like! Let's see how far you get.

char_237_gravel_CN_032.voiceText: Sorry… did I… mess up again…?

char_237_gravel_CN_033.voiceText: Looks like there's a lot of good hiding places here in this room!

char_237_gravel_CN_036.voiceText: Yes. I'm right here, always and forever.

char_286_cast3_CN_001.voiceText: Thank you for choosing Castle-3! I am honored to serve as your assistant, Doctor.

char_286_cast3_CN_002.voiceText: Doctor, please do not be intimidated by my appearance. My sturdy metal shell, modified by Master Closure herself, will make you invincible on the battlefield.

char_286_cast3_CN_003.voiceText: Warning: be careful not to strike my case too hard. It may damage me.

char_286_cast3_CN_004.voiceText: The topography in the wild may be treacherous, but Castle-3 is fitted with an engine with outstanding performance and a 4WD mode, to whisk you away from danger.

char_286_cast3_CN_007.voiceText: Doctor, if your life is ever in danger, just summon Castle-3! Castle-3 was created specifically for combat purposes. I am a top-class defensive warfighting robot.
char_286_cast3_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_286_cast3_CN_008.voiceText: Castle-3 is overjoyed to work with you. If you have a target that needs to be eliminated, Doctor, Castle-3 will gladly do it for you.
char_286_cast3_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_286_cast3_CN_009.voiceText: Castle-3's official manager is "Master Closure,"but please understand that you are even more important to Castle-3 than Master is, in most cases. I am your devoted, trustworthy battle companion!
char_286_cast3_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_286_cast3_CN_010.voiceText: Entering sleep mode. Press any button to wake.

char_286_cast3_CN_011.voiceText: Hello, Doctor. Thank you for choosing Castle-3. Tap anywhere to initialize startup options.

char_286_cast3_CN_012.voiceText: Firmware upgrade complete. Restart required. Please click anywhere to restart.

char_286_cast3_CN_017.voiceText: Device scan complete. All communications working as normal. Castle-3 is on standby, awaiting your orders.

char_286_cast3_CN_018.voiceText: Understood. Castle-3 is your best choice, Doctor, to lead a squad against enemy formations!

char_286_cast3_CN_019.voiceText: Next, Castle-3 will show you its true power as an industrial battle platform!

char_286_cast3_CN_020.voiceText: Enemy unit located. Ready for attack.

char_286_cast3_CN_026.voiceText: Enemies, you are forbidden to advance.

char_286_cast3_CN_028.voiceText: Doctor, that was at last a worthy opponent!

char_286_cast3_CN_029.voiceText: Well done, Doctor. Castle-3 is your best choice on the path of justice!

char_286_cast3_CN_030.voiceText: What an exciting battle! Let's fight together again next time.

char_286_cast3_CN_031.voiceText: Is everyone all right? I hope Castle-3's performance has exceeded your expectations.

char_286_cast3_CN_032.voiceText: I will hold up the rear. Everyone, retreat!

char_286_cast3_CN_033.voiceText: Is there anything Castle-3 can help with?

char_286_cast3_CN_036.voiceText: Doctor, would you like to grab a drink together? I might not be able to actually have a drink, but I can still treat you to one. It is fine, Master Closure will pay.

char_285_medic2_CN_001.voiceText: Do you need medical assistance, Doctor? You look quite energetic, though...

char_285_medic2_CN_002.voiceText: Doctor, you have been working far too late these days. Please get adequate rest, or Dr. Kal'tsit may give you an earful next time she sees you!

char_285_medic2_CN_003.voiceText: Please tell me where you feel uncomfortable. I could also do an examination, if you like.

char_285_medic2_CN_004.voiceText: You've worked hard. How would you like a cup of coffee, Doctor? I'd also like a sip of that coffee... but I can't... so I'll just have to be satisfied watching you enjoy yours.

char_285_medic2_CN_007.voiceText: I've printed out the standard blood test report I just did for you. Everything looks normal, but there's a very unique characteristic about your blood...
char_285_medic2_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_285_medic2_CN_008.voiceText: What do I like? I like "lovely Ms. Closure."Why, you ask? Uh... I'm not sure either! That's what my settings have been ever since Ms. Closure first initialized me...
char_285_medic2_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_285_medic2_CN_009.voiceText: I only feel useful when someone's sick or injured. But as long as you're healthy, as long as I get to be by your side... I'm okay with being useless! I'll still feel safe.
char_285_medic2_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_285_medic2_CN_010.voiceText: Doctor, I made a recording of you snoring just now! Your sleep quality is normal. The length of your REM sleep cycle is—

char_285_medic2_CN_011.voiceText: Hello, Doctor. You want me to say something more interesting to you? I'm afraid I have nothing interesting to say. I'm just a medical robot...

char_285_medic2_CN_012.voiceText: Firmware upgrade complete. Restart required. Please click anywhere to restart.

char_285_medic2_CN_017.voiceText: Medical supplies: confirmed. Battery charge: confirmed. Ready to deploy.

char_285_medic2_CN_018.voiceText: I'm pretty cumbersome... not much I can do besides providing emergency treatment and healing. Yet you still want me to be the captain?

char_285_medic2_CN_019.voiceText: Deploying. I hope no one gets injured.

char_285_medic2_CN_020.voiceText: Be careful, everyone! Leave the first aid to me.

char_285_medic2_CN_029.voiceText: With every battle, ever more soldiers are injured. When will humans finally stop hurting each other?

char_285_medic2_CN_030.voiceText: Well done, Doctor. That was a tough one. The enemies looked sickly, don't you think? Can I treat them too?

char_285_medic2_CN_031.voiceText: Is everyone okay? Hold still, I'll perform first aid on your wounds.

char_285_medic2_CN_032.voiceText: Don't worry, we've successfully retreated. However... I'll have to clean your wounds now. It might hurt, please be brave!

char_285_medic2_CN_033.voiceText: "Lovely Ms. Closure" told me that you need help here.

char_285_medic2_CN_036.voiceText: I asked "lovely Ms. Closure" to change "what I like the most" to you, Doctor. But she refused to do it... Waaahhh...

char_285_medic2_CN_042.voiceText: Welcome back, Doctor. You are in good condition. Keep it up!

char_192_falco_CN_001.voiceText: Don't worry, Doctor. No matter what happens, I'll protect you.

char_192_falco_CN_002.voiceText: Liberi have excellent eyesight. According to legend, some can even tell one droplet from another in a rainstorm. Sounds incredible, huh?

char_192_falco_CN_003.voiceText: I take everyday life too seriously? My apologies. I think that comes from my time serving as a Laterano Guard. I'll work on that in the future.

char_192_falco_CN_004.voiceText: To most Lateranos, heavy armor doesn't serve much of a purpose. Of course, when we perform the large-scale rituals of our homeland, we do dress up in ceremonial garb.

char_192_falco_CN_005.voiceText: I appreciate your faith in my abilities, Doctor. I won't let you down.
char_192_falco_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_192_falco_CN_007.voiceText: Right... I submitted a request to the HR office... to become your personal bodyguard. I guess maybe I miss my old job too much...
char_192_falco_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_192_falco_CN_008.voiceText: I grew up in Laterano and didn't really have the chance to learn about other cultures. Here in Rhodes Island, I get to see such diversity, way beyond my imagination. It's quite nice...
char_192_falco_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_192_falco_CN_009.voiceText: I have no regrets. Yes, true, they did drag me out of Laterano against my will... but this has been a great adventure. I've enjoyed it.
char_192_falco_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_192_falco_CN_010.voiceText: It is my duty to protect you, Doctor. Rest assured.

char_192_falco_CN_011.voiceText: My name is Plume, formerly of the Pontifica Cohors Lateran. I will be your sword, and your wings, as I defend your very life.

char_192_falco_CN_012.voiceText: Ah, so tactics can help you overcome a more skilled opponent, huh?

char_192_falco_CN_013.voiceText: Thank you, Doctor. As your bodyguard, your approval is the best award I can ask for.
char_192_falco_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_192_falco_CN_018.voiceText: As the leader, it's my responsibility to keep everyone safe.

char_192_falco_CN_025.voiceText: You think you're faster than me?

char_192_falco_CN_026.voiceText: No move can escape my sight!

char_192_falco_CN_027.voiceText: My resolve lies with my spear!

char_192_falco_CN_028.voiceText: I fight for the glory of Laterano!

char_192_falco_CN_030.voiceText: Like a wave crashing against an immovable stone, isn't it?

char_192_falco_CN_031.voiceText: Regroup! I'll look out for the remaining enemies!

char_192_falco_CN_036.voiceText: Doctor... it feels like I'm abusing my position...

char_278_orchid_CN_001.voiceText: I'll make the arrangements. Just leave it to me.

char_278_orchid_CN_002.voiceText: Doctor, I certainly hope my teammates won't cause any trouble while I'm here working for you... Aagh, the more I think of it the worse this headache gets!

char_278_orchid_CN_003.voiceText: An ordinary job, a peaceful life. That's all I ever wanted.

char_278_orchid_CN_004.voiceText: Nah, it's not that I don't get along with the other A6 members... I just get a headache whenever I see them!

char_278_orchid_CN_005.voiceText: ...My group is a whole mixed bag of craziness. Some of them get in trouble every day. Some are anti-social. Some never listen. And some are awfully stubborn. It's just impossible to get everyone to settle down and work...
char_278_orchid_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_278_orchid_CN_007.voiceText: I don't know how I ended up on this team either! All I wanted was an ordinary life. Why did I end up in charge of these... problem children?! Wait, Midnight is a grown man!
char_278_orchid_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_278_orchid_CN_008.voiceText: Popukar... needs a pat on the head. Catapult... needs to be tied up. Spot... just don't make him mad. Midnight... knocking him out is the only way to make him behave. There, Doctor, now you know the proper protocol for dealing with Team A6.
char_278_orchid_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_278_orchid_CN_009.voiceText: I made a cake for my teammates. You want to try, Doctor? They love my fruitcakes. Those A6ers really are a bunch of kids, aren't they?
char_278_orchid_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_278_orchid_CN_010.voiceText: Not a lot of time left today. Done with your work for the day, Doctor?

char_278_orchid_CN_011.voiceText: Captain of Reserve Op Team A6, Orchid, reporting in. Are you Dr. {@nickname}? Nice to meet you.

char_278_orchid_CN_012.voiceText: I learned a lot from this video. I'm sure it will be helpful in the future.

char_278_orchid_CN_013.voiceText: Thank you so much. I'll work hard to improve my skills from now on and strive for better results for you!
char_278_orchid_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_278_orchid_CN_017.voiceText: I'll complete my mission to the best of my ability.

char_278_orchid_CN_018.voiceText: Please follow the tactical combat manual closely, everyone. I'd appreciate it!

char_278_orchid_CN_019.voiceText: The battle has begun! Be careful, everyone!

char_278_orchid_CN_020.voiceText: Please follow the plan, everyone! Spread out!

char_278_orchid_CN_028.voiceText: I already have enough work to deal with!

char_278_orchid_CN_029.voiceText: Well done, Doctor! Impeccable leadership even against such a tough opponent.

char_278_orchid_CN_030.voiceText: Yes! Well done! We earned a good rest.

char_278_orchid_CN_031.voiceText: ...We need to work harder next time.

char_278_orchid_CN_032.voiceText: Is everyone okay? Let's get out of here!

char_278_orchid_CN_036.voiceText: Huh?! Overtime again?! Ugh, I knew it...

char_278_orchid_CN_042.voiceText: Morning, Doctor. Let's bang out today's work.

char_235_jesica_CN_001.voiceText: I-is there anything I can help with? Just name it and I'll do it.

char_235_jesica_CN_002.voiceText: Franka and Liskarm are so awesome! I really admire them. I want to become as great as they are someday. I can do it! Will you help me, Doctor?

char_235_jesica_CN_003.voiceText: Uh, I heard that Vanilla is here too? She was in my squad when she first joined BSW. We went on missions together! She's become a cool, reliable Operator now... but I'm still just me...

char_235_jesica_CN_004.voiceText: Dr. {@nickname}, do I look... spineless? I know I shouldn't let people walk all over me... I'm trying to change...

char_235_jesica_CN_005.voiceText: Sometimes I feel like I'm still in BSW, even after all I've been through with Rhodes Island. I'm not the old me anymore, either... strange. Is it because I really miss those days? No, no. I don't miss the person I used to be, that's for sure...
char_235_jesica_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_235_jesica_CN_006.voiceText: Hard work doesn't mean anything without results. At least that's what I think! That's why I don't want anybody to see me training alone. Just you, though... you watching me feels really comforting for some reason.
char_235_jesica_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_235_jesica_CN_007.voiceText: I pulled a muscle training a couple days ago... but don't worry, I-I'm okay! Urk! I won't bother anyone over this little thing, Doctor!
char_235_jesica_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_235_jesica_CN_008.voiceText: Freeze, hands in the air! ...Oh, did I scare you? Franka told me to be bold and assertive, and I was just experimenting... I'm really sorry...
char_235_jesica_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_235_jesica_CN_009.voiceText: Everyone at BSW and Rhodes Island is really amazing and talented. I know that I'm nothing compared to them... but, still, I really like getting compliments every once in a while!
char_235_jesica_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_235_jesica_CN_010.voiceText: Doctor... Doctor? Are you sleeping? I'll clean up your desk for you, then...

char_235_jesica_CN_011.voiceText: Um, are you Dr. {@nickname}? Nice to meet you. I'm Jessica from BSW. Sorry... I'm really bad at introducing myself...

char_235_jesica_CN_012.voiceText: This seems a lot more effective than training by myself.

char_235_jesica_CN_013.voiceText: Doctor... I'm... I'm so happy you're honoring me... Just... let me cry it out for a few minutes, I'll be fine...
char_235_jesica_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_235_jesica_CN_014.voiceText: Ah, Doctor, you think I'm a great Operator? Thank you so much for all your help. You motivated me most of all!
char_235_jesica_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_235_jesica_CN_017.voiceText: Just give your orders and I'll carry them out!

char_235_jesica_CN_020.voiceText: I'll definitely prove myself this time!

char_235_jesica_CN_028.voiceText: I'll show them what I can do!

char_235_jesica_CN_029.voiceText: I'm going to climb to the top of the mountain. I won't stop halfway!

char_235_jesica_CN_030.voiceText: I... I really did it? I managed to protect everyone by myself?

char_235_jesica_CN_031.voiceText: I could do better! I can't get complacent just because we won!

char_235_jesica_CN_032.voiceText: Requesting medevac! I dragged everybody down... it's all my fault! Sorry! I'm sorry!

char_235_jesica_CN_033.voiceText: The people at Rhodes Island, are they nice?

char_290_vigna_CN_001.voiceText: Hey, Doctor! I'm watching a concert! You're blocking the TV! I missed the best part!

char_290_vigna_CN_002.voiceText: You get people who say things like "fight the power" and "be true to yourself." But for us Sarkaz, that's just life.

char_290_vigna_CN_003.voiceText: I like bands... no, I LOVE bands! Of course, as a guitarist, I know every beat, every chord is important. But you gotta practice, practice practice. That's how you give the audience the ultimate face-melting solo!

char_290_vigna_CN_004.voiceText: So I'm nice to everyone, except I give you crap? Well, yeah. Doctor, you're in charge of so many people. You gotta be hard on yourself. Of course I'm gonna be hard on you too!

char_290_vigna_CN_005.voiceText: Hmm, this smell... is this the lunchbox Hibiscus brought you? You want me to eat it for you? No way! This... this wasn't in my job description!
char_290_vigna_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_290_vigna_CN_006.voiceText: If there's something you want out of life, you gotta work hard for it. Like, I want to become stronger, so I train. I want to have a deadly sharp weapon, so I customize the one I got. People talk like they do, but I'll keep working as hard as I can to get what I want!
char_290_vigna_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_290_vigna_CN_007.voiceText: Wha?! It's pouring outside? But I can't cancel my concert just 'cause it's outside! You can't stop me, I'm going! It's just a little thunder, it can't kill the passion I have for music!
char_290_vigna_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_290_vigna_CN_008.voiceText: You got an important mission you want me to handle? Hehee, you can count on me! Let's see here... "You are to acquire the following products for Rhodes Island during a time-limited mega-sale...?" Th-that's impossible!
char_290_vigna_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_290_vigna_CN_009.voiceText: Even if the crowd starts booing, the show must go on. You can't quit in the middle of a performance just because you messed something up. It's just like Sarkaz and Infected. We can't give up now, we can't just let them win.
char_290_vigna_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_290_vigna_CN_010.voiceText: Hey, you can't sleep over here! Ugh… you're too heavy for me to carry…

char_290_vigna_CN_011.voiceText: Excuse me, is this the office of Dr. {@nickname}? Could you please tell the Doctor that I'm looking for—what? YOU'RE the Doctor? All right, then. Operator Vigna, reporting in!

char_290_vigna_CN_012.voiceText: You gotta be willing to sweat a lot to keep up with battle tempo, is that right?

char_290_vigna_CN_013.voiceText: My new elite medal looks pretty boss, huh? Yeah, let's get a picture to celebrate.
char_290_vigna_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_290_vigna_CN_014.voiceText: I might not be that strong... but lemme show you what I can do with this spear!
char_290_vigna_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_290_vigna_CN_017.voiceText: I hope to learn a lot from everyone.

char_290_vigna_CN_018.voiceText: I may be the team captain, but you can all let me know where and how I might improve.

char_290_vigna_CN_029.voiceText: No matter how tough the bad guys are, I won't stop thrashing. Not like, a music thing. It's a battle thing.

char_290_vigna_CN_030.voiceText: Good job, everybody! Oh? Are you feeling left out, Doctor? You'll have to wait 'till we get back~

char_290_vigna_CN_031.voiceText: We cannot relax yet! Hold formation!

char_290_vigna_CN_032.voiceText: Ugh... This can't be it. We have to fight harder!

char_290_vigna_CN_033.voiceText: Is there a soundproof practice room here? I got guitar practice!

char_290_vigna_CN_034.voiceText: What are you doing? Stop touching me!

char_290_vigna_CN_036.voiceText: D-don't pat me on the head! It might make me shorter!

char_289_gyuki_CN_001.voiceText: Doctor, you gotta be hungry! Try some of my onigiri. They're great!

char_289_gyuki_CN_002.voiceText: I've actually got a lotta hobbies. They go way beyond martial arts. I'm also really into soccer, and flower arrangement. Wouldn't want you thinking I'm just some kinda bloodthirsty monster!

char_289_gyuki_CN_003.voiceText: My race eats other races? That's some old crap! Who told you that? Pff, what kinda coward goes around talking that crap behind my back? I'll give 'em a peace of my mind when I find 'em.

char_289_gyuki_CN_004.voiceText: My body? Heals right up whenever I get hurt. Even in the middle of a fight, the wounds close right back up. Handy, huh.

char_289_gyuki_CN_005.voiceText: Hey, Doctor, Rhodes Island's got a soccer tournament! Let's sign up together. When you got me on your team, it's in the bag, don't worry. Doctor, you better start thinking up a cool victory pose!
char_289_gyuki_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_006.voiceText: You don't even recognize me on the battlefield? I just start cutting through enemies one by one with a blank expression on my face? Wow! Sounds hella badass! Wish I could watch myself out there.
char_289_gyuki_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_007.voiceText: I got this problem where I kinda end up breaking stuff, so I'm working with my flower arrangement teacher to control my strength. Being around all those pretty flowers makes me real happy too.
char_289_gyuki_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_008.voiceText: Strategy? Ehh, not really my specialty. That's why I keep hopping right into the enemy's plans. But with you, Doctor, you always stop me before I screw up too bad. Been a big help!
char_289_gyuki_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_009.voiceText: I've always been pretty gullible. It's almost gotten me killed. But now I, Matoimaru, swear loyalty to you, Doctor! I know you'll never betray me, Doctor!
char_289_gyuki_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_010.voiceText: Grrr... Hey, no falling asleep, Doctor! You gotta listen to my stories or I'm gonna die of boredom!

char_289_gyuki_CN_011.voiceText: Matoimaru has officially joined Rhodes Island! You let me do the fighting and I'll take the orders, Doctor!

char_289_gyuki_CN_012.voiceText: Hey now I can beat 'em even harder.

char_289_gyuki_CN_013.voiceText: Doctor, you put my strength to good work and I'll be a happy lady!
char_289_gyuki_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_014.voiceText: Doctor, stand back a bit. I don't wanna hurt you swinging my naginata around. I, Matoimaru, will bring victory in the name of the Doctor!
char_289_gyuki_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_289_gyuki_CN_017.voiceText: Hah hah! You all look pretty strong. Let's do some warm-ups!

char_289_gyuki_CN_018.voiceText: Ugh, you want me to play captain? That means I get to beat 'em as hard as I want, right?

char_289_gyuki_CN_019.voiceText: You guys ready to rumble? We'll wipe the floor with 'em.

char_289_gyuki_CN_020.voiceText: Sorry to keep you waiting, bad guys!

char_289_gyuki_CN_025.voiceText: You're standing up to Matoimaru. Ballsy.

char_289_gyuki_CN_029.voiceText: A sea of fire and a mountain of blades... That was awesome! It's the battlefield I've always dreamed of!

char_289_gyuki_CN_030.voiceText: Doctor, I got 'em all! Hey, what happened here? Everything's busted. Did I do that?

char_289_gyuki_CN_031.voiceText: I'll get 'em before they escape! Can't call the battle over until I do!

char_289_gyuki_CN_032.voiceText: Retreat! I'll cover your escape. Make sure you don't get hit!

char_289_gyuki_CN_036.voiceText: You look happy about something. You gotta tell me too!

char_277_sqrrel_CN_002.voiceText: Intheinterestsofsafety, Iaminspecting escaperoutes and firefightingequipment. Onemomentplease.

char_277_sqrrel_CN_003.voiceText: Pleasebeaware, itisagainstregulation tolightfires or smokecigarettes inthecorridors. Thankyouforyourcooperation, Operators.

char_277_sqrrel_CN_004.voiceText: Ensuringawareness of firesafety and firefightingprotocols isakeypart ofmyduties. Allowmeto beginwithyou, Chief.

char_277_sqrrel_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_277_sqrrel_CN_006.voiceText: Um... Thetruthis... I'mverynervous... AndIdon'tknow whattosay... Chief, thankyouverymuch, foryourconcern.
char_277_sqrrel_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_277_sqrrel_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_277_sqrrel_CN_008.voiceText: Chief, canyoupleasehelp changethislightbulb... I... can'treachit... Oh, it'sworkingnow. Thankyou.
char_277_sqrrel_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_277_sqrrel_CN_009.voiceText: Chief... Theytheythey're barbecuinginthedormagain. Canyouplease stopthemforme! Aaaah! Someoneswapped myfireextinguisher withIfrit'sflamethrower! Areyouokay, Chief?
char_277_sqrrel_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_277_sqrrel_CN_014.voiceText: Thisis... anelitemedal? Ah! Yes! Iwillcontinue todomybest foreveryone, andfortheChief!
char_277_sqrrel_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_291_aglina_CN_001.voiceText: Dr. {@nickname}, I made this really strong coffee with our new coffee machine. Wanna try? You can only have one cup a day, though. Don't want you up all night!

char_291_aglina_CN_002.voiceText: Being a transporter isn't easy. The sender and the receiver always have their own reasons for getting involved... and whatever you're delivering could have something crazy inside. If you only worry about getting your stuff there on time, you could end up dead.

char_291_aglina_CN_003.voiceText: My mother was from the Far East, so my name doesn't sound very Siracusan. A lot of people ask me if it's even my real name, so I decided to use Angelina as a codename too.

char_291_aglina_CN_004.voiceText: Good morning, Dr. {@nickname}! Yeah, I'm off to send out some files. Dr. Kal'tsit said that my abilities could come in super useful on the battlefield... but I like bringing letters where they belong a lot more than I like fighting!

char_291_aglina_CN_005.voiceText: I actually don't know if I'm a good fit for Rhodes Island... I mean, a lot of really heavy stuff happens here, I don't know if I can handle it. Croissant comforts me all the time, but I don't know about myself sometimes. Am I really cut out for this?
char_291_aglina_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_291_aglina_CN_006.voiceText: I don't feel lost anymore. It's not that I'm any more comfortable with you or Rhodes Island... it's just that, as a transporter, it's my job to jump the gaps between tall buildings, right? And as a Rhodes Island Operator, I will bridge the gap between the Infected and Uninfected too!
char_291_aglina_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_291_aglina_CN_007.voiceText: Memories are precious things. I always remember that the Infected, just like us, look forward to a better tomorrow. I don't know anything about your past memories, Dr. {@nickname}, but I promise to help you find them, if you lost them.
char_291_aglina_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_291_aglina_CN_008.voiceText: Dr. {@nickname}, don't be shy, come closer! That's right! Three, two, one, sorridi! See? It's a photo sticker of you and me. The perfect souvenir, right? I guess it's also a symbol of... some of my feelings, haha.
char_291_aglina_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_291_aglina_CN_009.voiceText: The view from up on the deck is great. Especially for stargazing! See that lone star over there? People always say that one day, its companion star will appear, and then they'll embrace and dance together. Still... how long does it have to wait for the other one to show up? And how long do I have to wait... for the stars to grant my wish?
char_291_aglina_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_291_aglina_CN_010.voiceText: Hmm hmm! Mmm!♪Turns out coral lipstick is best!

char_291_aglina_CN_011.voiceText: I'm Angelina Ajimu, a transporter from Siracusa. You can just call me Angelina. Can I call you Dr. {@nickname}?

char_291_aglina_CN_012.voiceText: The battlefield is an ugly place... but I'll try not to let you down.

char_291_aglina_CN_013.voiceText: Since you trust me this much, Dr. {@nickname}, I have to work much, much harder than I usually do! Like, Siracusan transporters always say: "the slow are just dust in the wind."
char_291_aglina_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_291_aglina_CN_014.voiceText: I've made my decision. As long as you‘re still working to help the Infected, Dr. {@nickname}, I'll follow you. You've come so far, done so much... now it's my turn to do something for you, Doctor.
char_291_aglina_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_291_aglina_CN_017.voiceText: I'll give it all I've got, in work or in battle!

char_291_aglina_CN_019.voiceText: I might not be the best, but I'll still do what I can.

char_291_aglina_CN_025.voiceText: You got something weighing on you?

char_291_aglina_CN_026.voiceText: We gotta get out of this.

char_291_aglina_CN_027.voiceText: I'll show you what I can do.

char_291_aglina_CN_028.voiceText: Wanna see how it feels to float?

char_291_aglina_CN_029.voiceText: What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, right?

char_291_aglina_CN_030.voiceText: We all worked hard for this. Dr. {@nickname}, you'll remember it too?

char_291_aglina_CN_031.voiceText: Well, even I lose a letter sometimes...

char_291_aglina_CN_032.voiceText: The more difficult the situation is, the harder we have to try!

char_291_aglina_CN_033.voiceText: This place is like home to me!

char_291_aglina_CN_036.voiceText: My hair looks nice? Of course! I've got a secret. Wanna know what it is?

char_009_12fce_CN_001.voiceText: Forgive me, Doctor... There are limits to what I can do, including in conversation... but I'm honored to be your assistant. I look forward to helping you with your work.

char_009_12fce_CN_002.voiceText: Doctor, time heals all wounds. Please have more confidence in yourself. Your Operators have chosen to follow you because we believe that you will bring positive change.

char_009_12fce_CN_003.voiceText: Many Infected have relocated to Rhodes Island... not because they have any particular goals to achieve, but simply because they want a place to call home. The world outside no longer accepts them, after all...

char_009_12fce_CN_004.voiceText: Owl may not seem very friendly, but she's got a good heart. Don't worry about her.

char_009_12fce_CN_007.voiceText: 12F? That was the day I came to this world. You could say it's my birthday.
char_009_12fce_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_009_12fce_CN_008.voiceText: I might not be able to spend my entire life serving one person... but at least I can start working on it now.
char_009_12fce_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_009_12fce_CN_009.voiceText: She has finally found you, Doctor. What a perilous journey it's been. You're very important to her, as well as to everyone else.
char_009_12fce_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_009_12fce_CN_010.voiceText: I'll be by your side watching over you, Doctor, even in your sleep. So rest easy, you have nothing to fear.

char_009_12fce_CN_011.voiceText: You have my thanks for allowing me to join you. I will do my best to serve you, Doctor, from now on, with my alchemical skills. I have never had a name... but if you must call me something, you can refer to me as 12F.

char_009_12fce_CN_012.voiceText: I see, I understand now. Thank you for your guidance.

char_009_12fce_CN_017.voiceText: I may not possess outstanding skills, but I will do my best.

char_009_12fce_CN_018.voiceText: To make me Captain, to give me responsibility for this whole squad, is that really all right...? You have my thanks, Doctor.

char_009_12fce_CN_019.voiceText: Relax, Doctor. We will complete this operation in no time.

char_009_12fce_CN_029.voiceText: I'm already used to failure... but the losses truly make the victory sweeter. Don't they, Doctor?

char_009_12fce_CN_030.voiceText: This victory is all yours, Doctor. And I am honored to serve you, Doctor.

char_009_12fce_CN_031.voiceText: That was a hard-fought, hard-won victory, but we did it. Are you all right, Owl?

char_009_12fce_CN_032.voiceText: Failure is only normal. Don't be discouraged. I've been in many wars, and my experience tells me that your victory will come soon.

char_009_12fce_CN_033.voiceText: If you'd like, I can help. No trouble.

char_009_12fce_CN_036.voiceText: I am so thankful for all that you have done for me. I feel ashamed I have so little with which to repay your kindness. Forgive me, Doctor.

char_230_savage_CN_001.voiceText: Ahaha, Dr. {@nickname}! What can I do for you today?

char_230_savage_CN_002.voiceText: On a normal work day, I pretty much go around smashing things with my hammer, so it’s nice to get to do some paperwork like this every once in a while.

char_230_savage_CN_003.voiceText: When I worked for Rim Billiton, I took care of non-combat related jobs as well. For example, I did some mining and carried out geological surveys using electromagnets and stuff. Hmm... did that sound too complicated? In other words, I smashed up a bunch of stuff and dug up some other stuff!

char_230_savage_CN_004.voiceText: Amiya has a lot on her shoulders. If only I could help share her burden a little... By the way, Doctor, you must be tired too. Don't hesitate to let me know if there's anything you need help with!

char_230_savage_CN_005.voiceText: Providing cover, trailblazing, area denial... I might not be able to literally shield my teammates like the Defender Operators, but I can still protect everyone in my own way!
char_230_savage_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_230_savage_CN_006.voiceText: Did I… manage to keep everyone safe? Thank goodness! Doctor, please allow me to continue to stay with you and Amiya!
char_230_savage_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_230_savage_CN_007.voiceText: Doctor, want a cabbage veggie salad with mushroom pies? Yep, I made three servings! Yours, mine, and another for Amiya. She used to love the pies I made!
char_230_savage_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_230_savage_CN_008.voiceText: The running backs on the football field are unstoppable. They just keep charging forward in spite of everything, all to clear a path for their teammates. And then they just fall down and leave it to everyone else to finish the job. Isn't that sort of like what I do? It's very cool! I hope I don't have to get tackled though.
char_230_savage_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_230_savage_CN_009.voiceText: As long as I get to stay with you and Amiya, it's enough for me. Memories belong in the past, while the future is waiting for us to color it in. Amiya and I will continue to create more memories with you in the days to come!
char_230_savage_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_230_savage_CN_010.voiceText: Doctor, do you have a minute...? Then let's go get groceries so I can make dinner!

char_230_savage_CN_011.voiceText: I'm Savage, from Rim Billiton. As soon as I got the message from you and Amiya, I rushed right over to see what I could do. Huh? Doctor? You don't remember anything? Wow!

char_230_savage_CN_012.voiceText: Ooh, I see now. Uh huh! I understand everything.

char_230_savage_CN_013.voiceText: I feel a lot better taking orders from you, Doctor. I won't let you down!
char_230_savage_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_230_savage_CN_014.voiceText: Doctor, don't worry. No matter how many enemies there are, as long as you're with me, I'll smash 'em all!
char_230_savage_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_230_savage_CN_018.voiceText: I don't want anyone falling behind!

char_230_savage_CN_029.voiceText: Hmm, guess no mission is too difficult for us!

char_230_savage_CN_032.voiceText: It's too dangerous here! We have to fall back!

char_230_savage_CN_033.voiceText: Huh? You're really trusting me to do this kind of detail-oriented work?

char_230_savage_CN_036.voiceText: All done with work for the day!

char_282_catap_CN_001.voiceText: We got a lot to do today, Doctor. So how about we play some games first? Isn't getting nice and relaxed the best way to prepare for a hard day of work?

char_282_catap_CN_002.voiceText: Aw, I feel so lazy today for some reason! Maybe because Midnight isn't around? I love watching him chat up girls with that flashy smile of his. It's especially fun when the girls turn him down! Totally makes my day.

char_282_catap_CN_003.voiceText: Doctor, you know who's the most reliable in our group? Oh, you can't guess? It's Spot! He might be quiet, but he's very reliable. So, since there's so much work to do but only two of us... why don't we get him to come and help?

char_282_catap_CN_004.voiceText: Aw... Ms. Orchid yelled at me again today. She's such a nag! Must be work getting into her head and stressing her out. She should learn from me—I have the perfect balance between working hard and playing hard!

char_282_catap_CN_005.voiceText: Hey, where's Dobermann? She's out on business today? Yay, finally! I can slack off all day now, wonderful! I'm gonna go get some snacks first. Doctor, you want some chips or popcorn? I'll grab a bag for you!
char_282_catap_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_282_catap_CN_007.voiceText: Uh, Popukar, sweetie, please listen to me, I'll do anything you say, okay? J-just put down the chainsaw! Oh no, she's out of control! This is the worst! Doctor, run! Run! We gotta jump out the window! Yeah, the window! Follow me!
char_282_catap_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_282_catap_CN_008.voiceText: The town we were in back then... the mayor was a tyrant, a fat cat with no heart, no sympathy. Drove the townspeople nuts. I hated him too, so I blasted open his vault and handed out all the money I found to the townies. Now that was a good time!
char_282_catap_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_282_catap_CN_009.voiceText: I don't care what anybody thinks of me—it's more important I just enjoy every day doing what I like. My life belongs to me, so I alone decide what I do. Isn't that right?
char_282_catap_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_282_catap_CN_010.voiceText: Doctor... oh, you're asleep? Well, can't interrupt the Doctor's beauty nap, so I guess I'll go out and have some fun.

char_282_catap_CN_011.voiceText: Operation Reserve Team A6 member Catapult, reporting in! Hey, I can tell you're hella different from that stuffy old bit—I mean, that esteemed, honorable instructor Ms. Dobermann. Right? Like it's obvious!

char_282_catap_CN_013.voiceText: Hehe, I finally finished basic training. Wait, what? "After promotion, Dobermann will oversee further training..." No way!
char_282_catap_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_282_catap_CN_017.voiceText: It's not time to head out yet, right? Let me hang out for a bit longer...

char_282_catap_CN_018.voiceText: I'm the captain? I've been waiting forever to hear those words!

char_282_catap_CN_019.voiceText: Huh? Where did I leave my ammunition belt?

char_282_catap_CN_020.voiceText: Ugh, I hate fighting. But what else can I do?

char_282_catap_CN_029.voiceText: What an awesome formation, great tactics, it all went down perfect!

char_282_catap_CN_030.voiceText: I love commanders that lead us to victory—commanders like you!

char_282_catap_CN_031.voiceText: Relax, I set a whole bunch of traps right where the enemy's gonna be running. What? They didn't step in any of them? No way!

char_282_catap_CN_032.voiceText: Damn... we got no choice. Bug out!

char_282_catap_CN_033.voiceText: Hey, can take a peek and tell me if Dobermann's in there?

char_282_catap_CN_034.voiceText: You can't catch me! ...Oh, you can.

char_283_midn_CN_001.voiceText: Thank you for choosing me. Anything you'd like to say to me tonight?

char_283_midn_CN_002.voiceText: The Demon King of Higashi? Ahh, so you’ve heard about that… Well, the remnants of the past mean nothing to me. After all, an even more glorious future waits for me ahead.

char_283_midn_CN_003.voiceText: I may work in a different place now, but my job is still the same—to put a smile on everyone's face!

char_283_midn_CN_004.voiceText: I bet Ms. Orchid must have been born with a negative number on her happiness scale. Why else would she always look so stern, right? If you know anything about her, please tell me!

char_283_midn_CN_005.voiceText: I'm really skilled, you know! My swordsmanship training helps me maintain my figure and cultivate my elegance, which is why I practice with dedication every day. After all, even the powerful can weaken without constant training! That's a point worth remembering!
char_283_midn_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_283_midn_CN_007.voiceText: People used to say that I sold feelings as commodities, that I treated "happiness" as a product. Fools, all of them. Only by showing everyone my heart, can I get my customers to show me theirs!
char_283_midn_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_283_midn_CN_008.voiceText: I believe happiness is an infectious thing, a tangible atmosphere that truly exists. I reap happiness when others show me their hearts, and the others gain happiness from MY happiness.
char_283_midn_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_283_midn_CN_009.voiceText: My colleagues in team A6... they may be a bit weird, but they're truly kind souls. They're a gift from destiny, a gift that continues to remind me to cherish those important to me.
char_283_midn_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_283_midn_CN_010.voiceText: Now that I have some free time, I should read.

char_283_midn_CN_011.voiceText: Show me your brightest smile, esteemed customer! Happiness is at arm's reach when you're by my side. Midnight, at your service!

char_283_midn_CN_012.voiceText: It's important to never stop learning!

char_283_midn_CN_013.voiceText: Whoa, so my hard work really paid off! Let's set up a tower of champagne bottles to celebrate. My treat, of course!
char_283_midn_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_283_midn_CN_017.voiceText: With me on your side, success is guaranteed!

char_283_midn_CN_018.voiceText: Follow me! I'm cool, after all!

char_283_midn_CN_025.voiceText: O sword, slash this moonlit night open!

char_283_midn_CN_029.voiceText: You're really something, Dr. {@nickname}. You'll soon be shining brighter than me!

char_283_midn_CN_030.voiceText: There's only one thing that's impossible for me: being imperfect.

char_283_midn_CN_032.voiceText: No need to look back. We'll greet each other with a smile next time.

char_283_midn_CN_033.voiceText: A wonderful place. Let's have a drinking party tonight.

char_283_midn_CN_034.voiceText: Hey, don't mess up my collar.

char_283_midn_CN_036.voiceText: Thanks for taking care of me.

char_137_brownb_CN_001.voiceText: Boss, let's go grab a bite. You're buying. Huh? You bought last time? Nah, that don't sound right!

char_137_brownb_CN_002.voiceText: Use my head to win fights? Hmm... Hmm.. If I ain't strong enough to beat 'em down, I'll just train 'til I am. Nailed it!

char_137_brownb_CN_003.voiceText: Honey's sweet but getting it's a pain in the ass. I went for some the other day and the bees ate me for lunch.

char_137_brownb_CN_004.voiceText: My knucklers? My precious babies. Wouldn't have racked up all those wins without 'em!

char_137_brownb_CN_005.voiceText: There's a lot more to the underground fight scene than you might think. Lots of punks dove in before they had it figured out and ended up dead.
char_137_brownb_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_137_brownb_CN_006.voiceText: Oripathy? Who cares? Infected, Uninfected... They're all the same after I knock their lights out.
char_137_brownb_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_137_brownb_CN_007.voiceText: Huh? The fish in the kitchen? Hah! Right here in my belly now!
char_137_brownb_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_137_brownb_CN_008.voiceText: Huh? What's with all the names? Hah, use your brain, Boss! I gotta meet more people so I got more people to fight.
char_137_brownb_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_137_brownb_CN_009.voiceText: The only reason I joined the underground fight scene is 'cause I didn't have two dollars to rub together. But here on Rhodes Island I got that load off my mind. It's all thanks to you, Boss!
char_137_brownb_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_137_brownb_CN_011.voiceText: Yo! Boss, you know a winner when you see her! You got the world's strongest underground fighter, me, Beehunter!

char_137_brownb_CN_012.voiceText: I really don't wanna study. Send me out to fight already!

char_137_brownb_CN_013.voiceText: Hah hah hah! I got what I deserve!
char_137_brownb_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_137_brownb_CN_014.voiceText: You keep pushing me forward like this, and I ain't gonna let you down! Lemme show you what I can do in a fight, Boss!
char_137_brownb_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_137_brownb_CN_018.voiceText: Yeah! Chow's on me after we win this thing!

char_137_brownb_CN_019.voiceText: Relax, Boss. Ain't nobody can go three rounds with me!

char_137_brownb_CN_020.voiceText: So you're the ones looking for a beatdown. You guys?

char_137_brownb_CN_028.voiceText: Come on, is that all you got?!

char_137_brownb_CN_029.voiceText: The stronger the matchup, the more pumped I get!

char_137_brownb_CN_030.voiceText: Wiped the floor with 'em. What d'ya think, Boss? Look at 'em all piled up there!

char_137_brownb_CN_031.voiceText: That's a wrap. Let's head back and chow down!

char_137_brownb_CN_032.voiceText: Oof... Where's the Boss? Is the Boss okay?!

char_137_brownb_CN_033.voiceText: This room's a hell of a lot better than my usual digs!

char_137_brownb_CN_036.voiceText: You brought food? Yeah! You're the best, Boss!

char_164_nightm_CN_001.voiceText: Um, it's really bright in here... Doctor, do you think you could turn off some of the office lights? I'm not used to it yet...

char_164_nightm_CN_002.voiceText: Um, you really brought me here to be an Operator, right? Not to study me? What about that doctor, Miss Kal'tsit? What is she going to do to me...?

char_164_nightm_CN_003.voiceText: My staff was passed down to me by my father. Its magic does something called "Evernight" to those it touches. Anyone trapped in that illusion will... have trouble waking up the next day...

char_164_nightm_CN_004.voiceText: I'm used to being alone. When I feel lonely, I'll just talk to myself. Haha... Hmm? Is that weird?

char_164_nightm_CN_005.voiceText: Stare deeply into my eyes. Feeling sleepy, aren't you? Hehe... Now, how about you tell me where Rhodes Island stores its "Originium"?
char_164_nightm_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_164_nightm_CN_006.voiceText: Did you call me? Oh yes, my disease is worsening. That's because you wouldn't give me your "Originium," and now this body is gradually disintegrating... So, what should we do, Doc-tor?
char_164_nightm_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_164_nightm_CN_007.voiceText: Um, please let me apologize! I mean, erm, I m-might still end up saying something weird, but please don't get angry... I just have no way to control "her"...
char_164_nightm_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_164_nightm_CN_008.voiceText: Say, Doctor, if I were to suddenly end you, right here, how would everyone else react...? Argh! Grgh! No! I have to stop myself from... Hehe, I really would like to see it...
char_164_nightm_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_164_nightm_CN_009.voiceText: Doctor, don't you get tired of it, from time to time? Your work,life, feelings, everything... What would you say to just forgetting all of it, all at once? With my power, things like that can be arranged...
char_164_nightm_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_164_nightm_CN_010.voiceText: Your sleeping face is so cute, it makes me want to...

char_164_nightm_CN_011.voiceText: I'm Nightmare... Aah, that's a code name. My real name is Gloria. But, if you don't mind, I'd rather you call me that... I think my code name... is kind of scary...

char_164_nightm_CN_012.voiceText: You're making me stronger... but why...?

char_164_nightm_CN_013.voiceText: I came here as a patient, to get treatment for my disease. But now am I to understand that doctor wants me to fight for you?
char_164_nightm_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_164_nightm_CN_014.voiceText: Don't you think I'm only barely qualified for this promotion? It doesn't matter, I'm just lucky to be alive at this point. So whatever you want to do, we can do it.
char_164_nightm_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_164_nightm_CN_019.voiceText: What sorts of incredible powers will you be using? I can't wait to see~

char_164_nightm_CN_020.voiceText: So these are our enemies, huh? Looks fun.

char_164_nightm_CN_021.voiceText: Um, is there anything to eat?

char_164_nightm_CN_024.voiceText: Been a while since the last time I was on the battlefield.

char_164_nightm_CN_030.voiceText: Well, sorry, but this is the end I prepared for you.

char_164_nightm_CN_031.voiceText: We won. What more do you want?

char_164_nightm_CN_033.voiceText: I'll be fine in the corner...

char_164_nightm_CN_036.voiceText: D-did I do something bad again...? Just, please let me apologize. I'm so, sooo sorry...

char_220_grani_CN_001.voiceText: Reporting in, Dr. {@nickname}! Patrol completed. Nothing out of the ordinary!

char_220_grani_CN_002.voiceText: I'm starving. That battle really took a lot out of me... Huh? You got me something to eat? Just for me? A-apple pie! Thanks a lot! It looks great!

char_220_grani_CN_003.voiceText: Everybody here at Rhodes Island calls me "Tiny," but it really doesn't bother me. The boys back on the force always teased me the same way. Hey! Don't pat my head! Or my ears! Or face for that matter!

char_220_grani_CN_004.voiceText: {@nickname}, I might not make it to training on Wednesdays or Fridays... Right, I need to be out there doing my part to keep the peace, catching the bad guys! Huh? I have an important mission on Friday?!

char_220_grani_CN_005.voiceText: Rhodes Island has lots of strong Operators, but there's no one who can match my speed!
char_220_grani_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_220_grani_CN_006.voiceText: Where has the time gone? We've been working together so long now. {@nickname}, I will never forget everything we've been through. But we can't stop now! We have to keep striving for that bright future, don't we?
char_220_grani_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_220_grani_CN_007.voiceText: I just bumped into Skadi in the hallway... {@nickname}, you think she's cold and distant, don't you? She's actually very kind. Really!
char_220_grani_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_220_grani_CN_008.voiceText: Compared to everyone else, I'm pretty ordinary. I don't have any superpowers, or spectacular achievements to brag about... But I don't need magic or claws to make the world a better place. I can do that with my own two hands! Of course, we still have to eat well!
char_220_grani_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_220_grani_CN_009.voiceText: {@nickname}, you always worry so much about your people, but you never remember to take care of yourself. You can't do that! No matter what dangers you may face, I promise I'll be there to hold your hand! Definitely, you have my word!
char_220_grani_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_220_grani_CN_010.voiceText: Hmm? Why do you smell so good, {@nickname}? You're definitely hiding something tasty, aren't you?!

char_220_grani_CN_011.voiceText: Mounted Police Officer Grani has heard your cry for help! Fear not. From this point forward, I will protect you!

char_220_grani_CN_012.voiceText: I see. That's another thing I should watch out for. Uh huh!

char_220_grani_CN_013.voiceText: An elite promotion medal? For me? Thank you, {@nickname}! I'll hang it up with my police medal!
char_220_grani_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_220_grani_CN_014.voiceText: From the time I finished my first mission right up to this very day, my lance has been here to support me. As long as I grip it tight, my heart will have the courage it needs to protect the people and their dreams.
char_220_grani_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_220_grani_CN_017.voiceText: Shall I go scout the battlefield?

char_220_grani_CN_018.voiceText: You're making me the captain? Okay. I'll protect the whole squad!

char_220_grani_CN_019.voiceText: All right, let's bring home a victory!

char_220_grani_CN_025.voiceText: My lance will clear a path!

char_220_grani_CN_027.voiceText: In battle, someone must come out on top.

char_220_grani_CN_028.voiceText: My battlefield extends well above the ground!

char_220_grani_CN_029.voiceText: If you look to harm those under my protection, you'll have to go through me first!

char_220_grani_CN_030.voiceText: Nice! That was an excellent fight! You all did splendidly!

char_220_grani_CN_031.voiceText: {@nickname}, please stay close to me. There may still be some enemies around.

char_220_grani_CN_032.voiceText: Damn it... I can't let myself fall here!

char_220_grani_CN_036.voiceText: If we get the chance, I hope we can see the world together, {@nickname}.

char_263_skadi_CN_001.voiceText: I advise you to keep at least two meters away from me, for your own good. And of course you shouldn't speak to me either... I wouldn't want you to suffer on my account.

char_263_skadi_CN_002.voiceText: You've read my file? Terrible, isn't it? Indeed, if you stay near me, the same misfortune will befall you, and that's trouble for me too.

char_263_skadi_CN_003.voiceText: My hair is long and beautiful? Well, thank you... Would you like to touch it? It should be quite soft. I'm confident of that.

char_263_skadi_CN_004.voiceText: Could that be...? That woman, they call her Specter now, do they? Why is she dressed as a nun? Amnesia? That's awful... Dr. {@nickname}, you have to help her. She can't be allowed to forget her true function.

char_263_skadi_CN_005.voiceText: Oh you, how are you so tenacious? Then I suppose I have no choice but to defend you with all my might.
char_263_skadi_CN_005.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_263_skadi_CN_006.voiceText: Down beneath the vast blue sea, below the white waves that lap endlessly at the earth, lies all that I once held dear. I fear that one day misfortune will once again take someone important to me. That is why I fled. I don't want anyone I care about... to suffer on my account.
char_263_skadi_CN_006.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_263_skadi_CN_007.voiceText: Lovely, another easy day! No giant tentacles coiling up my friends, no blood crazed monsters hiding in the shadows... Just a straight fight on the battlefield. That's what I call easy!
char_263_skadi_CN_007.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_263_skadi_CN_008.voiceText: According to legend, my people have fought against the calamities for aeons. Perhaps we kept them from making landfall and terrorizing you city folk as well... So, how about buying me a drink, as a thank you?
char_263_skadi_CN_008.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_263_skadi_CN_009.voiceText: When you've made the long journey through the dark up to the water's surface, opened your eyes and had them filled with the glimmering light of a billion stars as the eternal undulation of the ocean waves caress your cheek, lapped the salty taste of your tears that remind you of your salty home, can you imagine what that tiny bathtub here at Rhodes Island might be like for me...? I'll have to show you my home someday.
char_263_skadi_CN_009.lockDescription: Improve Trust to check more info

char_263_skadi_CN_010.voiceText: You fell asleep? Well then, Dr. {@nickname}, have yourself a pleasant, dry dream.

char_263_skadi_CN_011.voiceText: I am Skadi, bounty hunter. Are you really hiring me? I cannot say what calamities I may bring with me.

char_263_skadi_CN_012.voiceText: So this is how you fight. Rush in with "woosh," knock them down with a "pow," and finish them with a "thud." Very good. I'll keep it in mind.

char_263_skadi_CN_013.voiceText: So this is the promotion Rhodes Island folks are always going on about? Not bad. Feels like I've actually become stronger, maybe.
char_263_skadi_CN_013.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 1 to check more info

char_263_skadi_CN_014.voiceText: Your thirst for power really does trouble me... But if you do indeed have the strength of will, then prepare yourself well, and we will stand together against the infinite darkness.
char_263_skadi_CN_014.lockDescription: Promote to Elite 2 for more info

char_263_skadi_CN_017.voiceText: I am quite skilled at teamwork too, however...

char_263_skadi_CN_018.voiceText: You're placing their lives in my hands?

char_263_skadi_CN_019.voiceText: Where's the sport when all the enemies are human?

char_263_skadi_CN_020.voiceText: You are nothing compared to the calamities I fought against.

char_263_skadi_CN_023.voiceText: I'll show you the dance of the depths.

char_263_skadi_CN_025.voiceText: Who knows what lurks within the kelp forest?
